edu.cnm.deepdive.teamsamurai.controller

Class CompleteController

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.teamsamurai.controller.CompleteController

  • @RestController
 @ExposesResourceFor(value=Complete.class)
 @RequestMapping(value="/completions")
public class CompleteController
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines REST endpoints for servicing requests on Complete resources, invoking CompleteRepository methods to perform the required operations.
